title: Milestone 1
text: The Psyche spacecraft was launched on Oct 13, 2023, and is expected to arrive there by July 2029.

title: Milestone 2
text: Psyche as big as Massachusetts, 3x as small as Arizona.

title: Milestone 3
text: The Psyche spacecraft uses a solar electric propulsion system, the first of its kind, which emits a cool blue glow while it's launched.

title: Milestone 4
text: The surface gravity on Psyche is much less than it is on Earth; therefore gravity on Psyche makes lifting a car feel like lifting a dog!

title: Milestone 5
